# Solontsy, Republic of Buryatia

}}
Solontsy () is a rural locality (a selo) in Tarbagataysky District, Republic of Buryatia, Russia. The population was 642 as of 2010. There are 10 streets in the locality.
Geography
Solontsy is located 17&nbsp;km north of Tarbagatay (the district's administrative centre) by road. Selenga is the nearest rural locality.
